# PPE unified run (operator + agents)

**Operator (human):** after agents complete SELECTION, run **`run_ppe.cmd`** from repo root only. Optional: `run_ppe.cmd --dry-run`, `run_ppe.cmd --status`.

**Agents (steward BUILD):**

1. At **SELECTION**, update [`docs/SOP/ACTIVE_PHASE_MANIFEST.json`](docs/SOP/ACTIVE_PHASE_MANIFEST.json): `phasePlanPath`, `sprintSpecPath`, `status: READY` ([`ACTIVE_PHASE_MANIFEST.md`](docs/SOP/ACTIVE_PHASE_MANIFEST.md)).
2. **Refresh Google Docs** before a new cycle: optional `refresh_google_docs.cmd`; `run_ppe.cmd` also runs **cycle-start** refresh automatically ([`GOOGLE_DOCS_REFRESH_V1.md`](docs/SOP/GOOGLE_DOCS_REFRESH_V1.md)).
3. Tell the operator: run `run_ppe.cmd` (do not ask them to hand-edit HANDOFF/FRONTIER or paste orchestrator logs).
4. After phase exit: read `artifacts/orchestrator/LAST_RUN_REPORT.md`; **cycle-end** refresh runs after closeout; review `artifacts/control_plane/google_docs_refresh_report.md` if needed; use a **new** Cursor thread with [`AGENT_CONTINUITY_BRIEF.md`](docs/SOP/AGENT_CONTINUITY_BRIEF.md) only ([`docs/CONTEXT_RULES.md`](docs/CONTEXT_RULES.md)).

**No active chapter:** manifest `COMPLETE` + empty `phasePlanPath` is normal — do SELECTION before `run_ppe.cmd`.

Canonical runbook: [`docs/SOP/RELAY_ORCHESTRATOR_RUNBOOK_V1.md`](docs/SOP/RELAY_ORCHESTRATOR_RUNBOOK_V1.md).
